    "body": "\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Metal backend configuration now properly disables on non-Apple platforms to avoid code generation mismatches.\n  * Metal target detection improved with consistent platform-independent checks.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added test coverage for Metal code generation with multiple data types: float32, float16, and int32.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
